Comments:	Installation:
		1) load nvidia-glx.tcz
		2) exit to prompt
		3) create xorg.conf
			sudo Xorg -configure
		4) move new config file to /etc/X11/ and name it to xorg.conf
			sudo mv xorg.conf.new /etc/X11/xorg.conf
		5) sudo nvidia-xconfig
		6) startx
		7) add etc/X11/xorg.conf to backup (/opt/.filetool.lst)

		If you already have Xorg installed and have xorg.conf skip steps 3-4.

		If you don't have xorg.conf then you can skip steps 3-4 if you load pkg-config and procps extensions for once only.

		For testing your installation you can run glxgears.
		
		For more information please refer to nvidia-glx-doc extension (index.html).

